increased, and that is--

00:31:43.500 --> 00:31:44.953
Will Goetzmann:
 That sounds like

00:31:44.953 --> 00:31:45.849
irrational exuberance.
 

00:31:45.849 --> 00:31:48.390
Okay.
 

00:31:48.390 --> 00:31:54.608
It's easy to say that they're
irrational.

00:31:54.608 --> 00:31:57.279
It's harder to say that they're
rational.

00:31:57.279 --> 00:32:03.096
It would be nice to know
