You're not saying that subprime
incomes are going up,

00:32:52.170 --> 00:32:54.160
but you're saying the approvals
are going up,

00:32:54.160 --> 00:32:56.387
so something has to fill that
gap in the purchase price and

00:32:56.387 --> 00:32:58.308
that means they're being more
