00:32:58.308 --> 00:33:00.298
Will Goetzmann:
 Yeah, I think that there's

00:33:00.298 --> 00:33:02.288
some evidence consistent with
your observation.

00:33:02.288 --> 00:33:06.481
It's amazing how much you can
get off staring at a graph like

00:33:06.481 --> 00:33:10.605
that because buried behind it
