this is from Seattle,
and what we've done here is

00:33:23.390 --> 00:33:28.432
we've gone from 2006--
what we've done is we've said,

00:33:28.432 --> 00:33:33.740
"Let's extrapolate the
housing price in 2006,

00:33:33.740 --> 00:33:37.182
let's extrapolate it and then
