00:38:41.956 --> 00:38:45.429
Stata--some people use that.
 

00:38:45.429 --> 00:38:47.210
What else do you need to run an
econometric model?

00:38:47.210 --> 00:38:53.630
This isn't a trick question.
 

00:38:53.630 --> 00:38:59.958
You have a blue scarf on,
what do you need to estimate a

00:38:59.958 --> 00:39:02.030
model like this?
 

